"title": "6241: seduction",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6241",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The deliberate enticement or persuasion of someone into the abandonment of godly principles. Scripture speaks of both sexual and spiritual seduction.</p>\n<h2>Sexual seduction</h2>\n<h3>Warnings to avoid temptation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:1-Prov7:22\">PRO 7:1–7:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:22\">2TI 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:10\">PRO 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:16-Prov2:19\">PRO 2:16–2:19</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of enticement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:6-Gen39:12\">GEN 39:6–39:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:1-Num25:3\">NUM 25:1–25:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:15-Num31:16\">NUM 31:15–31:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:1\">JDG 16:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:4-Judg16:5\">JDG 16:4–16:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:1-2Sam11:4\">2SA 11:1–11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:1-1Kgs11:6\">1KI 11:1–11:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:14-Rev2:16\">REV 2:14–2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:20-Rev2:22\">REV 2:20–2:22</a></p>\n<h3>The law as a deterrent</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:16-Exod22:17\">EXO 22:16–22:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:4\">HEB 13:4</a></p>\n<h3>Resisting temptation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:1\">JOB 31:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:14\">MAL 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:27-Matt5:30\">MAT 5:27–5:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:2-1Cor7:3\">1CO 7:2–7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:8\">PHP 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3-1Thess4:6\">1TH 4:3–4:6</a></p>\n<h2>Spiritual seduction</h2>\n<h3>Through Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1\">GEN 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44\">JHN 8:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:11\">2CO 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:3\">2CO 11:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:14\">2CO 11:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11\">EPH 6:11</a></p>\n<h3>Through lying spirits and false prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1\">1JN 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:19-1Kgs22:23\">1KI 22:19–22:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:18-2Chr18:22\">2CH 18:18–18:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1\">1TI 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:24-Matt24:25\">MAT 24:24–24:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:22-Mark13:23\">MRK 13:22–13:23</a></p>\n<h3>Through false teachers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1\">2PE 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:14-2Pet2:15\">2PE 2:14–2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:6-2Tim3:7\">2TI 3:6–3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:13\">2TI 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:18-1John2:19\">1JN 2:18–2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:7-2John1:8\">2JN 1:7–1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:10-Jude1:12\">JUD 1:10–1:12</a></p>\n<h3>The need for vigilance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:21-1Thess5:22\">1TH 5:21–5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:28-Acts20:31\">ACT 20:28–20:31</a></p>\n<h2>The process of seduction</h2>\n<h3>A thought planted</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:2-Gen3:3\">GEN 3:2–3:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:3\">MAT 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:14\">JAS 1:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:15\">1JN 2:15</a></p>\n<h3>An advantage promised</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:4-Gen3:5\">GEN 3:4–3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:6\">MAT 4:6</a></p>\n<h3>Attraction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:6\">GEN 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:16\">1JN 2:16</a></p>\n<h3>Persistence on the part of the seducer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:8-Matt4:9\">MAT 4:8–4:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:9\">GEN 19:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:15-Judg16:16\">JDG 16:15–16:16</a></p>\n<h3>Yielding</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:6\">GEN 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:15\">JAS 1:15</a></p>",
